<br>
After all, in the course of fighting, those other melees will take hits.  Spells from the mob, momentary agro grabs, etc.  In theory they'll be smart enough not to get reposted.  None the less, those classes need a little healing.  At top level, they'll have self healing methods, but at lower levels, letting them heal 6 hp per hit helps a lot, especially on fully hasted duel wielders.<br>
